<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_b9ab0867011e.aspx"><b>诗经·陈风·月出</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonb9ab0867011e">
<p>月出皎兮，佼人僚兮。舒窈纠兮，劳心悄兮。<br />月出皓兮，佼人懰兮。舒忧受兮，劳心慅兮。<br />月出照兮，佼人燎兮。舒夭绍兮，劳心惨兮。<br /></p>
